  <brief_title>Accurate Controlled Dental Sedation</brief_title>
  <acronym>ACDS</acronym>
  <official_title>The Clinical Efficacy of the Combination Target Controlled Infusion With Bispectral Index Monitor in Propofol Sedation for Dental Patients With Mental Retardation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
