  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Participants aged 16 or over,

          2. American Society of Anesthesiologists (ASA) physical status 1 or 2

          3. The treatments of dental caries, endodontics, periodontics and prosthesis were planed

          4. Participants had moderate or severe Mental Retardation, and were not completely
             cooperated with dental treatment

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients could communicate and cooperate with dental treatment, but used dental
             sedation for decrease of the anxiety and the fear about dental treatment or another
             reasons,

          2. Patients needed premedication

          3. Patients had uncontrolled or sever medical condition
      </textblock>
